  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221130/extras/eae27002e076ab8d701dbad76ae82b3e.avif?t=1763388854\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>Jump Adventures is a minimalistic platformer game. Prepare for a bite-sized adventure across vibrant worlds, each with their own challenges and dangers waiting to surprise you!<br><br>Embark on a short, but sweet journey that can be completed in one sitting.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221130/extras/about_gif.GIF?t=1763388854\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221130/extras/98e89763c66197a2cf43d731ead86447.avif?t=1763388854\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>Immerse yourself in hand-drawn visuals, dynamic orchestral soundtrack that reacts to in-game events, and mystic ambient sound cues.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221130/extras/atmosphere_gif.GIF?t=1763388854\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >…and more!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <i>Customization</i>: choose your unique look from a variety of unlockable skins, colors and trails.<br></li><li> <i>Statistics</i>: view your in-game stats!<br></li><li> <i>Steam Achievements</i>: can you unlock them all?</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221130/extras/eae27002e076ab8d701dbad76ae82b3e.avif?t=1763388854\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>Jump Adventures is a minimalistic platformer game. Prepare for a bite-sized adventure across vibrant worlds, each with their own challenges and dangers waiting to surprise you!<br><br>Embark on a short, but sweet journey that can be completed in one sitting.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221130/extras/about_gif.GIF?t=1763388854\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221130/extras/98e89763c66197a2cf43d731ead86447.avif?t=1763388854\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>Immerse yourself in hand-drawn visuals, dynamic orchestral soundtrack that reacts to in-game events, and mystic ambient sound cues.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221130/extras/atmosphere_gif.GIF?t=1763388854\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >…and more!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <i>Customization</i>: choose your unique look from a variety of unlockable skins, colors and trails.<br></li><li> <i>Statistics</i>: view your in-game stats!<br></li><li> <i>Steam Achievements</i>: can you unlock them all?</li></ul>",
